            <p>Some <span class="line-through">unemployed</span> dude learning how to develop for the
                web.</p>
            <p class="my-4">
                <ion-icon name="location-outline" class="text-orange-600"></ion-icon> Orem, Utah
            </p>

            <p>Born and raised in <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iXfbS0vXqYo">Utah</a>. I first started
                writing some basic HTML for a <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Yu-Gi-Oh!">Yu-Gi-Oh!</a>
